text: Paweł Gaca (5 October 1917 - 11 August 2008) was a Polish gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1917 births Category:2008 deaths Category:Polish male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Poland Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:People from Wodzisław Śląski
